creator: Benjamin Ayesu-Attah
descriptionHtml: Tired of trying to do math in your head at the checkout line? Let our app do the heavy lifting for you! With our trusty tax calculator, you can simply enter the price of your item and the tax rate, and boom - we'll give you the exact amount of tax you owe. No more fumbling with a calculator or trying to figure out complicated formulas. Plus, with a sleek and user-friendly design, our app is sure to impress even the most math-averse individuals. So why wait? Try our tax calculator today and kiss those pesky math problems goodbye!
